lead_paragraph: Shortly after Philadelphia 76ers president and general manager Bryan Colangelo said he is not actively shopping any of his players, Sixers center Nerlens Noel openly wondered how he, Jahlil Okafor and Joel Embiid can co-exist as the team's three big men.

headline.print_headline: 76ers Center Noel: Too Many Bigs on Team,' Just a Logjam'
headline.main: 76ers Center Noel: Too Many Bigs on Team,' Just a Logjam'
